    "body": "This issue will track the tasks needed to prepare the infrastructure we'll need to support automated testing and provisioning of source and binary packages.\r\n\r\n- [x] Acquire AWS account credentials\r\n- [x] Setup spending alerts\r\n- [x] Review Kubernetes setup documentation at https://kubernetes.io/docs/setup\r\n- [x] Develop an initial EC2 host allocation based on installation requirements.\r\n- [x] Deploy a minimal EC2 host allocation for development and testing.\r\n- [x] Develop provisioning scripts and tools to automate the cluster setup process.\r\n- [x] Deploy production allocation using developed scripts.\r\n- [ ] Develop a retention policy for source packages.\r\n- [ ] Develop a retention policy for binary packages.\r\n- [ ] ? @tgamblin @scheibelp (setup build bot?)\r\n\r\nThe following issues should be considered blocked on this work:\r\n#7121\r\n#7123\r\n#7116\r\n#7117",
